{"about_the_game":"<br><br><strong>Otto and the Ancient Worlds</strong> is an 8-bit 2D adventure platformer about an archeologist who discovers an ancient library filled with magical books. Each book contains a living story of a mythology or folklore, and a mysterious evil figure releases them into Otto\u2019s world! Otto must return the mythology and folklore back to their books and destroy this unknown evil in the process.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>- Game Features -</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as the archeologist Otto, and use his whip to uncover artifacts and explore forgotten worlds in a stunningly beautiful 8-bit adventure.<br></li><li> Fight your way through 6 selectable stages, each with a unique world and boss.<br></li><li> Find the hidden outfits in each stage to give Otto a special ability.<br></li><li> Each stage is based off of a historical mythology or folklore from stories all around the world.<br></li><li> Encounter a vast variety of historical figures from mythologies and folklore to help you in your journey.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731985919","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731985919","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863720/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731985919","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863720/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731985919","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":1323850,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<br><br><strong>Otto and the Ancient Worlds</strong> is an 8-bit 2D adventure platformer about 